      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next big project! This vehicle is the perfect choice for a dedicated restorer or someone looking for a valuable source of parts. While it has seen better days and will require a fair amount of work to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a classic model at an entry-level price. Bring your tools and your vision to give this car a brand-new lease on life!",
