    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a collector-grade example that will satisfy the most discerning buyer looking for a factory-new experience.",
      "price": 49500.0,
