    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound, starts reliably, and handles smoothly on the road. The interior is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat, and all electronics are fully functional. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find a few small stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches from normal use. It is a dependable, high-quality car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to the most exacting standards of preservation. This vehicle exhibits flawless exterior surfacing and an interior environment that retains its original factory integrity. Mechanically, the powertrain operates with absolute precision, reflecting a history of rigorous preventative maintenance and climate-controlled storage. This offering represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a vehicle in peerless, showroom condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
